{"tid":631203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[克林頓呢咁？］科米︰特朗普嫖妓講大話 「道德不合格」 不宜當總統","createTime":"2018-04-16T09:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T12:24:53.000Z","uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"03e662f6b23cb510724af4b3bb08e92c5fe10baa","tid":631203,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T09:08:06.000Z","msg":"美國聯邦調查局（FBI）前局長科米（James Comey）遭總統特朗普批評後反擊，形容對方道德不合格（morally unfit），不尊重女性和謊話連篇，不適合擔任總統，呼籲國民以選票表達對他的不滿。<br />\n<br />\n科米接受艾國廣播公司（ABC）訪問時表示，特朗普曾澄清外界懷疑他多年前在俄羅斯嫖妓的指控，稱他沒在莫斯科的酒店過夜。惟科米認為，俄羅斯有可能已掌握他嫖妓的證據來威脅他。<br />\n<br />\n科米又批評特朗普把所有女性視作洩慾對象，不斷在大小事情上欺騙美國人，作為總統是「道德不合格」。<br />\n<br />\n通俄門調查上，科米認為現有證據顯示有人妨礙司法公正，又透露特朗普曾問他是否效忠自己，但科米重申僅忠於美國人民和制度。<br />\n<br />\n雖然科米批評特朗普措辭嚴苛，但不認為國會該彈劾特朗普，因此舉將導致美國社會混亂，但鼓勵國民踴躍投票，以選票表達價值觀。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普此前於Twitter批評科米，稱他沒有效執行職務，是有史以來最差的FBI局長，又表示與他不相熟，從來沒問他是否效忠自己。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://inews.hket.com/article/2051379/科米︰特朗普「道德不合格」%20不宜當總統\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2051379%2F%E7%A7%91%E7%B1%B3%EF%B8%B0%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E3%80%8C%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%88%E6%A0%BC%E3%80%8D%2520%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%9C%E7%95%B6%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1&d=0955fzHkKFo8gU5cknr%2BFzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=53e52c33\" target=\"_blank\">http://inews.hket.com/article/2051379/科米︰特朗普「道德不合格」%20不宜當總統</a>"},{"pid":"8733537f111d6451c83c30b7809b443436b9f338","tid":631203,"uid":158613,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:05:23.000Z","msg":"民主黨人另計"},{"pid":"38dab7ccf94c946232fce93bd8df2b81208255e6","tid":631203,"uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:11:34.000Z","msg":"克林頓就係因為呢啲野俾人彈劾喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bda5abc767b1111e981ec9fd2884b224481b866","tid":631203,"uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:18:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Y2WfMWq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FY2WfMWq.jpg&h=99705d68&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e1887ea17e329011da7e294f3127ef8b662dd5a","tid":631203,"uid":26752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8733537f111d6451c83c30b7809b443436b9f338","tid":631203,"uid":158613,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:05:23.000Z","msg":"民主黨人另計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T12:21:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcSGn-a0J5O-HIxx6vYHVwRcRFsDJ0KCbYlPByxSC5-g81EpKrb8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcSGn-a0J5O-HIxx6vYHVwRcRFsDJ0KCbYlPByxSC5-g81EpKrb8&h=186e44bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f37661f14e26652616e1db0f18a9a19f626c57f1","tid":631203,"uid":26752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T12:24:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/766359fe89ede2afda0ba9a212836512/tumblr_oscsmqQiyu1vbkvgoo1_500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2F766359fe89ede2afda0ba9a212836512%2Ftumblr_oscsmqQiyu1vbkvgoo1_500.jpg&h=93ab72a1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}